			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				 <br>  <br> Please I am looking for players opinion on this. The last 3 nights while in Hib/nimue I notice a complete epidemic of the focus pull groups out there. From the formor dungeon entrance, coruscating mine 4 pit spots, the 3 finis spots in CF, the siabra city, the waterfalls in SI, the warsades in EZ, ever single spot was camped with a focus pull group leveling their buff bolts, alts and guild mates. I was depressively impressed by this epidemic; I know that it is the fastest way to xp but I personally don&#8217;t like it.  <br>  <br> I don&#8217;t want to make any judgment about them if they are good or bad to the realm or call to any nerf. I just gona express my felling: I am sick of it, it is boring, annoying and making leveling in HIB for new comers almost impossible. And I left the realm of hib to roll a savage over them, I could not take this crap anymore.  <br> 
