			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				focus pull is no where near the fastest way to lvl, the focus spells dmg leeches exp from the group members. best exp group to maximize exp and pull rate is  <br>  <br> 3 shield tanks with guard on each other  <br> 1 druid <br> 1 bard <br> 2 mana enchanters/elds <br> 1 person getting PLed <br>  <br> the reason focus pulling works so well for PLing bots is that it requires far less people  <br>  <br> mana chanter <br> druid  <br> bard <br> 1-2 mana enchanter/eld &lt;--- if you dont have at least one of these the exp is ALOT slower then just making a normal group <br>  <br>  <br> this leaves room for 3 or 4 people to get PLed where as the other formation leaves only one spot for PL, this is the reason why this is the prefered method. i can assure you that a good tank group will do better on overall exp and as they lvl up assuming they arent all 50
