			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				Heres the solution, there HAS to be at least 3-4 ppl near the same level as you, who arent in a focus group, seek them out, be polite and form your own group. Go to a spawn that is rarely camped, there now you can get good xp (of course not as fast as focus) and not have to succumb to being a focus pull whore. My 8 man group used tank PBAE from 10-50 and we leveled faster then any focus pullers, except for lvl 50 groups p lvling peeps.
