pens once in a blue moon)  <br>  <br> Personaly i would not shed a tear if FP was nerfed or taken away in my opinion it's not beneficial to the game ( if you main for FP is that it reduces leveling time then maby you should argue that mythic should reduces leveling post level 40 ) <br>  <br> 
